<h3><a href="/vnews/display.v/ART/46cded66ba1c3">Gradebook Access</a></h3>
<div class="socs-feature-text">
<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Avery ISD is pleased to announce the release of Ascender's Parent Portal to view students' grades and attendance.  If you already have an existing account in txConnect don't worry just enjoy the new application as your existing username and password are still valid. The old web address will no longer work. You will have to use the new url. </span></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>  </span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>NOTE: The old mobile site will no longer work. This new url will work with whichever device you will be using.</span></span></strong></p>

<p><span style="font-size:22px;"><u><strong><a href="https://txeis08.txeis.net/ParentPortal/login?distid=194902" target="_blank">You may access the new portal here</a></strong></u></span></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"> </p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Ascender Parent Portal does require the email address associated with your parent/guardian account to be on file with the office to allow you to utilize the <u>email/text alert feature</u> in Ascenders' Parent Portal.</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Please send the email address that will be associated with a parent/guardian Parent Portal account to your campus office or email them to parent.portal@averyisd.net. </span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>Be sure to include student name(s) associated with these email addresses.</span></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"> </p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;">NOTE: Student portal accounts will not have alert options at this time.</span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"> </p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><u><span style="font-size:22px;"><strong><span style='font-family:"Times New Roman",serif'>There is a button for quick access at the top of all pages of our website for the Parent Portal.</span></strong></span></u></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"> </p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><a href="/vimages/shared/vnews/stories/46cded66ba1c3/Avery%20PP%20Brochure.pdf" target="_blank">GUIDE TO NEW ASCENDER PARENT PORTAL SET UP</a></span></strong></p>

<p style="margin-right:0in; margin-left:0in"> </p>

<p class="msonormal" style=" line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;">If you sign up to receive notifications, they will be coming from AveryISD@ascendertx.com. </span></strong></p>

<p class="msonormal" style=" line-height: normal;"><strong><span style="font-size:20px;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Please add this address to your contacts or approved e-mail recipients so they will be allowed through to your inbox.</span></span></strong></p>

<p class="msonormal" style=" line-height: normal; text-align: center;"><strong><span style=" font-family: Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 13.5pt;">**********</span></strong></p>
